== IPMC Learning Path

The Incubator PMC (IPMC) oversees podlings and mentors.  
This path provides background and exercises for effective participation.

[.small]
*Key:* 📘 Guide 🖥️ Slide Deck 🎞️ Video 🧩 Quiz 🧠 Practice / Scenario

== Steps

1. 📘 **Read:** link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Incubator+PMC+Onboarding[Incubator PMC Onboarding]  
2. 🖥️ **Slide deck:** link:https://training.apache.org/presentations/apache/incubator/IPMC/index.html[IPMC Onboarding]  
3. 🎞️ **Watch:** link:https://youtu.be/e2Vcf4U-f08[IPMC Onboarding]  
4. 🧩 **Quiz:** link:https://canvas.instructure.com/enroll/N33MBP[IPMC Onboarding Quiz]  
5. 🧠 **Practice:** link:https://canvas.instructure.com/enroll/C8994Y[IPMC Scenarios Training]

