=== Governance & Community Health
- 📘 link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Governance+in+Practice[Governance in Practice] — guidance on applying ASF governance principles in podling communities  
- 📘 link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Vendor+Neutrality[Vendor Neutrality] — ensuring projects remain independent of single-vendor control  
- 🖥️ link:https://training.apache.org/presentations/apache/incubator/VendorNeutrality/index.html[Vendor Neutrality (Slide Deck)] — why balanced governance keeps Apache projects healthy and independent  
